f="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-game-awards-2023-winners-3555550">在此处</a>查看<em>NME</em>对 2023 年游戏奖的报道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/god-of-war-ragnarok-announces-new-valhalla-dlc-3555558">《战神诸神黄昏》后宣布新的《瓦尔哈拉》DLC</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
